Title: Mini Retro Game Console with Hundreds of Games
Body (HTML):
Immerse yourself in the nostalgia of classic, arcade style gaming with this retro mini game console. Pre-loaded with up to 600 vintage games, it connects directly to your TV for hours of fun.

Teach your kids the classic games from your childhood or relive the memories with your friends. With two controllers, you can enjoy hours of gaming battles with a pal!

Specifications:

Mini Retro Gaming Console

Includes up to 600 built-in classic games (please refer to images for list of games included)

With 2 controllers for hours of gaming battles

Great fun for friends & family

What's In The Box:

1x Game Console

2x Wired Controllers

1x Audio/Video Cable for TV

1x AUS Power Plug

1x USB Cable

1x User Manual

1x Game list
